$ DBA_COL_COMMENTS
@ dba_col_comments


code {
select
   column_name,
   comments
from
   dba_comments
where
   owner = 'RENE'          and
   table_name = 'TAB_XYZ'
;
code }

sa:

  → development/databases/Oracle/objects/tables/columns[Columns]

 `dba_tab_comments`

  → development/databases/Oracle/installed/data-dictionary
